result.name: 2018-biological-data-on-individual-squid-to-determine-population-dynamics-in-uk-waters
result.notes:
Measurements of statolith, beak, mantle, weight, sex, maturity and hatching 
dates for 106 individual squid (*Loligo vulgaris, Loligo forbesii, Illex 
coindetii*) caught in UK waters in 2018.
